CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

February 28, 2007

[Cite as 02/28/2007 Case Announcements, 2007-Ohio-724.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2006-2269. State ex rel. Prestwood v. Wolaver.
